{"tid":1678572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］依加立法會復會，可唔可以成為目標","createTime":"2019-10-27T17:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T17:45:47.000Z","uid":132544,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e92e198f3ba2ccf5cd7093bdc2e89cc6cb3fe53","tid":1678572,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"依加嘅街頭抗爭，點解無612、71咁勁<br />\n<br />\n係因為無個大目標<br />\n<br />\n變成咗裝修快閃<br />\n<br />\n最多攻擊政府合署等<br />\n<br />\n並無真係有明確嘅目標&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;對準政權<br />\n<br />\n容易失焦<br />\n<br />\n當然裝修快閃堵路都要繼續做<br />\n<br />\n我支持你地做<br />\n<br />\n但係依家哩啲抗爭手段已成公式<br />\n<br />\n要有突破<br />\n<br />\n一係有新抗爭形式<br />\n<br />\n唔好一味人鏈唱歌<br />\n<br />\n一係和勇升級<br />\n<br />\n我鳩嗡下<br />\n<br />\n例如罷工（無咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、武裝升級等<br />\n<br />\n一係就要搵個清晰明確嘅目標攻擊<br />\n<br />\n而我正想講嘅就係以立法會為目標<br />\n<br />\n不分和勇，示威者都有一個目標<br />\n<br />\n凝聚嘅力量一定比快閃、小型遊行強<br />\n<br />\n話雖如此<br />\n<br />\n入港島圍立會固然有好大嘅風險啦<br />\n<br />\n所以想係到討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"3c10a39d8bd462d40335a422fd67b3201f8b39af","tid":1678572,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77dce20757ae3f9d74711ee83c75c062f65c3663","tid":1678572,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"可能有人會唔同意<br />\n<br />\n屌我風向撚<br />\n<br />\n不過我都只係想討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c24b96c743eb1f7ebcdbe7bcd76369414333e0","tid":1678572,"uid":9160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"放晒水馬,入面又有狗,況且呢個時勢,聚唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42b665fafcd463d48151b5bbb138e2db8f1bf14","tid":1678572,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite